---
title: Spicy Pulled Pork & Green Pepper Wraps with Cheddar & Spicy Yogurt Sauce
description: Savory with a dash of heat—pulled pork is big on flavor when you’re short on time. Here it stars in lunch-friendly pan-toasted wraps that come together in just 15 minutes. You'll warm up the pork, adding green peppers and some spice, then pile it into soft tortillas with cheddar cheese. Wrap it all up, sear for the ultimate melty crispness, drizzle with tangy-spicy yogurt sauce, and you’re ready to roll in no time at all.
